 lines, we show that inhibition of XIAP has a non-linear effect on\nsensitization towards apoptosis induced by the BH3 mimetic HA14-1. This study\njustifies further ex vivo and animal studies on the potential of the treatment\nof leukemia and lymphoma with a combination of BH3 mimetics and XIAP\ninhibitors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 May 2011 17:04:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-05-13"}
